    "body": "Ok. I have an ORM model, the model refers to table, and instance refers to record. So when I display class, I want to see the create statement and even relationship between this table and others, and when I display instance, I want to see the columns and values of current record. So that's why I want `_ipython_display_` can be used in classes also.\n"
